flowchart TD
    Start([Start deployment]) --> Push[Push code to main]
    Push --> WaitCI[Wait for Publish to GHCR workflow]
    WaitCI --> VerifyPkgs[Verify packages on GitHub]

    VerifyPkgs --> Scp[scp deploy/ folder to VPS]
    Scp --> Env[Copy .env.example to .env]
    Env --> Config[Set GHCR_IMAGE_PREFIX, DOMAIN, CERTBOT_EMAIL]

    Config --> Login{Packages private?}
    Login -->|Yes| DockerLogin[docker login ghcr.io]
    Login -->|No| PullTest[docker pull test images]
    DockerLogin --> PullTest

    PullTest --> Init[Run ./init-letsencrypt.sh]
    Init --> Scale[Optional: scale worker=2]
    Scale --> Verify[Verify HTTPS, API, UI]
    Verify --> Done([Deployment complete])

    WaitCI -->|CI failed| FixCI[Fix build and push again]
    PullTest -->|denied / not found| FixPrefix[Fix .env prefix or GHCR auth]
    FixCI --> Push
    FixPrefix --> Config
